  { question: 'What areas do you serve in Malaysia?', answer: 'We serve all Malaysian states: Selangor, Kuala Lumpur, Johor, Penang, Perak, Pahang, Sabah, Sarawak, and more. Remote area application processing available online and via WhatsApp.' },
  { question: 'Can I try the excavator before committing to financing?', answer: 'For used excavators, we allow inspection and testing before final approval. Bring your operator to test the machine. We want you to be 100% satisfied with your equipment choice before signing.' },
